title: Best of The Herd for Oct 14, 2020

description:
-There's not much difference between Ryan Tannehill and Lamar Jackson

-Tom Brady has high standards because he is a winner and the Buccaneers aren't

-Le'Veon Bell made a mistake leaving a great Steelers organization

-Aaron Rodgers and Matt LaFleur are getting along because they're winning. What happens if they struggle?


Guests: Will Blackmon, 10 year NFL Veteran

Emmanuel Sanders, Saints WR
